#define GREETINGS ["You aren't even a footnote in history, %s. You're barely a blank page.","How long did it take you to get here, %s? I could have lived a dozen lifetimes in that span.","You’re slow. Everything about you is painfully, dreadfully slow, %s.","I wouldn't waste the speed force on you, %s. It would be a crime against efficiency.","Go. Run. It won't change your inevitable insignificance, %s.","I've seen the future, %s, and you’re nowhere in it.","You struggle so hard, %s. It's fascinating how much energy you waste just to exist.","Did you think you were fast enough to catch my eye, %s? You aren't.","I could end your timeline right now, %s, and no one would even remember you were here.","Don't blink, %s. You might miss the last few seconds of your relevance.","You're trying to defy the odds, aren't you, %s? The odds usually win.","I know exactly what you’re going to do next, %s. It’s almost boring.","You have potential, %s. Unfortunately for you, potential is perishable.","Step aside, %s. You’re standing in the way of destiny.","I’ve seen better efforts in the past, %s. Much, much better.","Finally, a moment of consistency. Tell me, %s, what do you think you’re accomplishing here?","You’re surprisingly persistent, %s. I wonder if that will be your undoing.","I’ve looked at your timeline, %s. It’s... adequate. For now.","Keep walking, %s. Let’s see how far you actually get before you hit a wall.","You aren't a threat, %s. But you are a curious distraction.","You actually managed to keep pace with my curiosity, %s. That’s an achievement.","I see you, %s. I see exactly where you're heading. It’s quite the path.","You’re more capable than you realize, %s. It makes me wonder if you’re worth the effort.","You have a certain gravity, %s. Don't let it pull you apart.","I’m intrigued, %s. Let’s see if you can handle the speed of the current moment.","Impressive, %s. You have a density to your existence that I haven't encountered in a while.","You’re a deviation, %s. A beautiful, unexpected knot in the thread of time.","You’re strong, %s. But are you fast enough to escape what’s coming?","I could learn to tolerate your presence, %s. If you play your cards correctly.","You have power, %s. Use it carefully. It’s so easy to break things that matter.","At last. An adversary worth the chronal effort. Welcome, %s.","I’ve checked every possible future, and you are the only one who keeps appearing, %s.","Such power... it ripples through time like a stone thrown in a pond. I’m impressed, %s.","We are the masters of our own paths, you and I, %s. Let’s see whose path lasts longer.","Don't try to outrun me, %s. I’ve already arrived at the end of your story, and I must say... it’s exhilarating."]

#define WrestleWin ["Did you feel that, %s? No? That's because I was already done with you before you even started.","How disappointing. I traveled through time just to be bored by you, %s.","You’re a footnote in history, %s. And not a very interesting one.","I didn't even have to vibrate my molecules to snap your neck, %s. How dull.","Go ahead and scream, %s. History won't remember you anyway.","You have such grand ambitions, %s. It makes your failure all the more hilarious.","I’ve watched you die a thousand times in a thousand timelines, %s. This one was just... tedious.","Look at you, gasping for breath. Does it hurt, %s? Good.","I am the villain of your story, %s. And you just reached the final chapter.","You were never a threat, %s. You were just a speed bump.","You fought well, %s. Almost well enough to be worth my time. Almost.","I’ve played this game before, %s. I always win.","Your hope was adorable. Let me crush it, %s.","You're smart, %s. But not smarter than the man who controls time.","I know everything about you, %s. Including exactly when and how you'll fail.","That was almost exciting, %s! Let's do it again—I can just go back and reset the clock.","You're a variable I hadn't accounted for. I don't like variables, %s.","A spirited defense! Too bad your future is already written, %s.","You almost got me there, %s! Almost. But you see, I've already won.","You're a bright light, %s. Let's see how fast I can make you burn out.","Now this is a challenge! I've missed the thrill of truly breaking someone, %s.","You're impressive, %s. It makes destroying you so much more satisfying.","I’ve been waiting centuries to see if you could actually put up a fight, %s.","You have power, %s. Let’s see what happens when I tear it away from you.","You're one of my favorite failures, %s. Don't die too quickly.","Finally! A real adversary! I'm going to enjoy watching you suffer, %s.","Your speed is impressive, %s. But my hate is faster.","You're the closest thing I have to a rival. Pity that you're nothing compared to me, %s.","Come back to the present, %s! Or stay in the past where you belong—in the grave.","You're a god among mortals, %s. And even gods bleed when I'm around.","At last! Someone who can actually keep up with the agony I inflict, %s!","You are my masterpiece of destruction, %s. I’m going to savor your defeat.","We could have been legends, %s. But I prefer to be the one who stands over your ruin.","History needed a tragedy, and you just provided it, %s. Perfection.","You are truly elite. And that’s exactly why I had to break you, %s."]

#define WrestleDefeat ["You got lucky, %s! I've already gone back and changed things so you never existed!","That wasn't me! You defeated a time remnant! Try again, %s!","You think you've won? I'm just getting started, %s.","This is a glitch! I'll fix this timeline, %s!","You're not worth my time anyway. I'm leaving, %s.","You've disrupted the timeline, %s. I will make you pay for that.","I'm not impressed, %s. I've seen better.","You're just a blip in the grand design, %s.","I'll be back, %s. And you won't even see me coming.","Victory? You? Don't make me laugh, %s.","You caught me off guard, %s. A rare and irritating occurrence.","You're faster than I calculated, %s. That's a problem I'll solve.","My speed is absolute, %s. You just found a lucky loophole.","I'll remember this, %s. And I'll come back for you.","You haven't won anything, %s. You've just delayed the inevitable.","You're persistent, %s. I hate that in an opponent.","You forced me to retreat. I don't retreat, %s.","I've analyzed this encounter. I will not fail again, %s.","You're an anomaly, %s. And anomalies get deleted.","Fine, you win today. But I control the clock, %s.","You're better than I thought, %s. I’m almost... interested.","You've bested me, %s. For now. I'm going back to fix that.","You have potential, %s. It's a shame you're destined for failure.","You forced my hand, %s. I won't be so gracious next time.","I'm impressed. Truly. Now leave before I change my mind.","You are truly a threat, %s. I'll have to deal with you personally.","You bested me. I haven't been this angry in centuries, %s!","You're a real rival, %s. I'm going to enjoy ruining you.","You've earned this win. But at what cost to your future, %s?","I yield this victory, %s. But I'll be back before you even realized I left.","You have truly matched me. This is... an unprecedented outcome, %s.","You are my equal. And that makes you my greatest enemy, %s.","Tactically brilliant, %s. You’ve earned my absolute hatred.","I have no choice but to concede. For now, %s.","You are the only person who can challenge me. I think I'll let you live, %s... just to see what you do next."]
